import React, { createContext } from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.scss'
import App from './App'
import reportWebVitals from './reportWebVitals'

import { GlobalVariablesContext } from './Context/GlobalVariablesContext'
import{ DataProvider } from './Context/DataContext'

const REACT_APP_URL = REACT_APP_URL + ''
const REACT_APP_GOOGLE_MAP_API = 'AIzaSyAtP9KGxPuB9C1sFEJqa9DDHSNn5UNLssI'

ReactDOM.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <GlobalVariablesContext.Provider value={{ REACT_APP_URL, REACT_APP_GOOGLE_MAP_API }}>
      <DataProvider>
        <App />
      </DataProvider>
    </GlobalVariablesContext.Provider>
  </React.StrictMode>,
  document.getElementById('root')
)

reportWebVitals()
